            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>white</strong> <strong>wine</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong>, 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> in a medium bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>cucumber batons </strong>to the bowl and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>zingy cucumber</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Set aside half of the cucumber batons to serve plain!</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
