    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat and add the <strong>brioche</strong> <strong>halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and charred</p><p>Set aside until serving and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
