    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>butterflied</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4 min on each side until golden, then turn the heat down to medium and cook for a further 4-5 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
